===Format===
'''Fight Night Pro Scrims:''''' June 18th - 22nd, 2023
** Squad {{Abbr/TPP}}.
** 24 teams.
* '''Semi Finals''' : ''June 18th
** 24 teams are divided equally into three groups of 8.
** Round-robin format.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16}} teams qualify for ''finals.
* '''Finals''' : ''June 20th
** 16 teams , 2 matchdays
** 6 matches.
** Map order : ''Erangel>>Miramar>>Erangel>>Miramar>>Erangel>>Miramar.
* '''TDM Battles''' : ''June 21st - 22nd
** 16 teams , 2 matchdays
** 2v2 TDM Battle
** ₹5,000 for every pan kill

